prompts.prompt: Build me a single page application called BluegrassID that can read HTTP requests from an external application, present an agreement with message "Please accept my agreement" with accept and decline buttons. When the accept button is clicked, the single page application should append the query parameter "agreement=yes" to the url of the external application and redirect it back to the requested URL. If the user clicks on decline then just print the message "You are not authorized to proceed."
